{"tid":209282,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港新四大天皇 白卡傷津公屋綜援","createTime":"2017-04-20T05:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T16:52:42.000Z","uid":79353,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7950a014610d6adad6e16b07e4c9e0648984ddd","tid":209282,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"玩晒啦<br />\n<br />\n有兩蚊車撘<br />\n<br />\n單人公屋好多人排十幾年都冇<br />\n雖然病人上樓要住過宿舍兩三年觀察下先<br />\n<br />\n津貼 100%傷殘好似有千九 二千<br />\n<br />\n綜援四五千<br />\n<br />\n單人公屋租金唔洗一千<br />\n<br />\n得閒去扮做義工呃下阿婆錢<br />\n<br />\n如果唔追求世俗意義上的成功<br />\n如果唔係餐餐大魚大肉<br />\n<br />\n都夠一人生活等死。"},{"pid":"0d1618653346b666a47d1f82ff773c770b132457","tid":209282,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:58:33.000Z","msg":"你地覺唔覺得而家呢個年代<br />\n<br />\n做到新四大天皇先係香港成功人士<br />\n<br />\n反正做唔到醫生都係死"},{"pid":"fb9d67fa4b9259c33db931ddca31e4037c2d523f","tid":209282,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"多謝cc台某人提出香港新四大天皇。"},{"pid":"49542221871a1ac4370ceb75adcb10c7e95f5c66","tid":209282,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"拎傷殘可以拎綜援架咩？"},{"pid":"cd55c62c1a937a1888557974f19f2407e86ae569","tid":209282,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎傷殘可以拎綜援架咩？</blockquote><br />\n咁點計都係綜援呃得多錢d"},{"pid":"ce26c0ce40726bd1169cf2a1cb11bc6e6ef36bb7","tid":209282,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"好彩我冇白卡"},{"pid":"533ef14f51891bc2efc5e26d7c04af87dd7719d1","tid":209282,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩我冇白卡</blockquote><br />\n我都冇"},{"pid":"13fcbee3542bc58e9618eb987539c329c9d9aed1","tid":209282,"uid":80416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:37:05.000Z","msg":"中學有幾個同學屋